        Female subjects ≥ 21 years of age:

          -  with a baseline diagnosis of apical vaginal or uterine prolapse;

          -  who had laparotomic or laparoscopic sacrocolpopexy, including robotic-assisted, for
             apical vaginal or uterine prolapse within 7 years of enrolment;

          -  where GYNEMESH PS Mesh was used as a bridging material, and;

          -  who are willing and able to participate in prospective follow-up.
